alerts.description:

extending from near Lomax to 14 miles west of Garden City, moving
southeast at 30 mph.

tree damage. Wind damage is also likely to mobile homes,
roofs, and outbuildings.

Locations impacted include...
Big Spring, Garden City, Forsan, Lomax, Big Spring Country Club, Big
Spring McMahon-Wrinkle Airpark, Elbow, and Spraberry.

This includes Interstate 20 between mile markers 161 and 175.
